## Limitations
This report is based on available data as of early April 2025. The dynamic nature of global oil markets and regional economic conditions means that gas prices can fluctuate rapidly. Additionally, the information is drawn from secondary sources, which may not capture all nuances of the market dynamics. Further, the lack of specific data on the exact impact of each factor limits the precision of the analysis.